## Installing via Helm Repo

1. Add Bee Repo
```console
helm repo add beeraspberry https://beeraspberry.github.io/helm-charts/
helm repo update
```

2. Install the chart via Chart Repo
```console
helm install <release name> 
```

## Uninstalling via Helm Repo
```console
need instructions
```

